Why you need LE02 leg extension and curl machine for leg day? 
“Pro"-is the answer. GMWD was shuttled to countless gyms and factories and tested it for over six months. If you want to get more sturdy thighs the right way, choose it. LE02 leg extension machine is the best value for money. 
What is the most memorable point in LE02's design process? 
In order to simultaneously achieve good support for the knees, keep the axis of motion parallel to the knees, and make the equipment accessible to most family members in home gym, engineers has tweaked the statistics for over 1 month. 
What's the latest update point of LE02? 
You can change the leg extension machine to the leg curl machine with a simple plug. The removable thigh holder creates more training possibilities. 
Why you should do leg extension and leg curl at home? 
The leg extension and the leg curl are valuable isolation exercises. Leg curls are a valuable addition to your leg-building workout. While this exercise may not adequately replace movements like the deadlift, it can perfectly supplement this routine. 
Does using this leg machine contribute to a more focused and efficient quad workout compared to other fitness equipment? 
Squats and deadlifts target the hamstrings and glutes alongside your quads. This machine can take away from maximum quad activation. Leg extensions isolate your quadriceps, ensuring they get the attention needed for increases in strength and size.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
RIMSports had its humble beginnings in a small living room in Queens, New York. What you see today is just because of the passion for fitness for Colin Raja, who was a national boxing medalist, and Angie, who trained in Muay Thai. 
We know what it takes to maintain a healthy lifestyle and are committed to this #fitnesslife 100%. We also innovate, design, manufacture and test all products before it gets to you! We also believe in hard work, dedication, innovation, and drive - these are the values that run RIMSports! 
WHY DO YOU NEED AN ARM BLASTER? 
Helps to keep correct posture during biceps curls, and triceps exercises.
Prevents arms from flailing or pointing outward during heavyweight curls.
Prohibits the ability to cheat your curls.
Reduces unnecessary stress put on arms when performing curls.
Provide much more protection and an efficient workout while lifting.
Increases the size of the muscle without causing quick fatigue.
Allows you to perform maximum reps in comfort and stability.
HOW TO USE IT? 
Wear around the neck 
Place the plate just below the chest; if not, adjust the straps to the ideal length position 
Rest your elbow right on the elbow pads 
Squeeze nice and hard 
CONTOURED DESIGN 
Our bicep blaster is uniquely constructed in a curved pattern design to comfort body shape and give a custom fit! 
PADDED SUPPORT 
To comfort your curling workouts, RIMSports has designed an arm blaster with dual padded elbow and neck pads to offer zero discomforts and a pain-free experience! 
ADJUSTABLE STRAP 
Premium grade webbed adjustable Nylon strap for easy length adjustment into the ideal position which helps increase your workout intensity and provides more stability! 
HEAVY-DUTY CONSTRUCTION 
Made of thick gauge lightweight aluminum and heavy-duty rivets for increased durability and to provide supreme stability in the utmost comfort! 
PREMIUM LOOK AND QUALITY 
Unlike other low-grade arm blasters, our bicep blaster has been made of premium quality materials for longer durability with appealing color and logo designs for a classy look. These arm blasters provide much more protection and an efficient workout while lifting. 
STRONG AND STURDY 
Our arm blaster is made of strong materials and fitments for advanced security and durability. It also focuses all movements in the bicep and tricep zone while lifting and gives you that massive pump you need! 
NOT JUST FOR BICEPS 
Since the arm blaster works the biceps so well, the other advantages of it were overlooked. But it is also a great tool for triceps and 21s' curls workout!

description: Product DescriptionThe Body-Solid Cam Series Biceps and Triceps Machine (GCBT380) features an intelligent dual-function design to help you develop bulging biceps and triceps muscles. Raise or lower the adjustable seat for proper body positioning, then drape your arms over the soft supportive pad, which is positioned at 30 degrees for precise biomechanical movement. Pull the oversized pop-pin to lower the lifting arm, grab the rotating V-bar handle, and start up your bicep preacher curl routine. Quickly reposition the V-bar to face upward to continue with a triceps workout. Made with a 2- by 3-inch and 2-by-4-inch supportive steel mainframe and double-stitched upholstery, this curl bench and triceps extension machine is durably constructed to stand up to rigorous use in gyms and clubs. It uses standard-sized weight plates or Olympic weight plates (with OA8 Olympic Adapter Sleeve) for resistance (weight plates sold separately). When assembled, the Body-Solid Cam Series Biceps and Triceps Machine measures 45 by 43 by 40 inches (L x W x H) and has a weight of 79 pounds. It is backed by the Body-Solid Lifetime In-Home and Full Commercial . Weight post is 1" dia. The Valor Fitness CB-6 Adjustable Arm Curl Bench is the ultimate solution for customizable arm workouts. Designed with full adjustability, this seated preacher curl bench provides five adjustable positions for the seat, armrest, and bar holder, ensuring a tailored fit for any user. Built with durable 2” x 2” steel, it offers unmatched stability during intense bicep training. The high-density, dual-layered vinyl padding adds comfort and support, reducing strain on arms and shoulders. Supporting up to 250 lbs for users and 200 lbs for the weight bar, the CB-6 is ideal for anyone serious about building bicep strength with precision. 
The Valor Fitness CB-31 Plate Loaded Arm Curl and Triceps Machine is a dual-function unit designed for both bicep curls and triceps extensions, making it a versatile addition to any gym. This plate-loaded curl machine features an adjustable sundial mechanism, allowing seamless transitions between exercises. Crafted with robust 2” x 2” solid steel, the CB-31 accommodates up to 150 lbs on its weight pegs, compatible with both 1” standard and 2” Olympic plates. Perfect for targeted arm workouts, it combines durability and versatility for effective upper body training. 
The Valor Fitness CB-11 Standing Arm Curl Station is a unique design tailored for users who prefer standing bicep curls. This standing preacher curl machine promotes proper form and effective muscle engagement, with a saddled seat pad for added comfort. Constructed from heavy-duty steel and designed to withstand rigorous use, the CB-11 provides a stable platform for focused arm training. With dimensions of 41” x 26” x 47”, this machine is compact yet robust, making it ideal for both home gyms and light-commercial fitness facilities. 
The Valor Fitness CB-5 Arm Curl Preacher Curl Station is a traditional preacher curl bench offering dual-position versatility for varied arm curling exercises. This dual-position arm curl bench allows users to perform curls on either side for an enhanced range of motion. Built with a heavy-duty 2” x 2” steel frame, the CB-5 delivers stability and strength during every workout. High-quality, dual-layered padding ensures maximum comfort while withstanding intense use. Measuring 45” x 31” x 45.75”, it’s a reliable choice for home or light-commercial gym settings. 
Each Valor Fitness arm curl bench provides specialized features to fit different training needs: 
CB-6 Adjustable Arm Curl Bench: Full adjustability for seated preacher curls with ergonomic support.
CB-31 Plate Loaded Curl and Triceps Machine: Dual-functionality for biceps and triceps with plate-loading versatility.
CB-11 Standing Arm Curl Station: Standing preacher curl machine for improved muscle engagement and form.
CB-5 Arm Curl Preacher Station: Traditional preacher curl bench with dual-position flexibility for targeted training.
Choose the model that aligns best with your fitness goals and workout preferences for effective and efficient arm training. 
Valor Fitness Preacher Curl Bench - Adjustable Seated Arm Curl Machine for Targeted Bicep Training 
Achieve exceptional bicep strength and definition, designed to support both beginners and advanced lifters. Built with a durable 2” x 2” solid steel frame, this bench delivers unmatched stability during intense arm workouts, ensuring your focus stays on building powerful biceps. Its heavy-duty construction resists wobbling or shifting, even under heavy loads, making it a reliable addition to any home gym or light-commercial fitness space. 
The adjustable arm pad and seat allow for customized positioning, accommodating users of all sizes for optimal comfort and support. The high-density, dual-layered padding reduces strain and provides ergonomic support, ensuring you can focus entirely on your form. Footed rubber end caps protect gym floors from scratches, keeping your workout space pristine. 
Perfect for preacher curls, concentration curls, and other targeted arm exercises, this preacher curl bench seamlessly combines durability, functionality, and comfort. 
Valor Fitness Standing Preacher Curl Bench - Adjustable Saddle Bench for Precision Arm Training 
Elevate your arm training with the Valor Fitness Standing Preacher Curl Bench, designed for optimal bicep isolation and superior muscle engagement. This adjustable saddle bench features a pivoting arm pad and ergonomically designed armrest, ensuring proper form and effective performance during every curl. Its sturdy construction and adjustable settings make it suitable for users of all sizes and fitness levels, offering a personalized training experience. 
Crafted from heavy-duty materials, this preacher curl bench provides unmatched stability, allowing you to focus on building strength without worrying about wobbling or shifting. The compact design integrates seamlessly into home gyms or light-commercial fitness setups, maximizing your space while delivering professional-grade performance. Ideal for preacher curls and concentration curls, this bench is perfect for those serious about sculpting powerful biceps and enhancing overall arm strength. 
Valor Fitness Standing Preacher and Spider Curl Arm Station - Dual-Position Bicep Training Bench 
The Valor Fitness Standing Preacher and Spider Curl Arm Station is the ultimate tool for targeting biceps with precision. Designed for both preacher curls and spider curls, its dual-position functionality helps isolate different areas of the biceps, delivering balanced and effective muscle development. Whether using a traditional grip, hammer grip, or an EZ curl bar, this versatile bench offers unmatched flexibility for various arm workouts, including dumbbell curls and forearm exercises. 
Built with a heavy-duty steel frame, this bicep curl bench ensures stability during intense workouts, while its ergonomic arm pad promotes proper form to reduce strain and maximize engagement. Ideal for home gyms and light-commercial fitness spaces, the compact design fits seamlessly into any workout area. Perfect for beginners and advanced lifters, this arm station supports your goals of building strength, enhancing definition, and achieving peak bicep performance. 
Valor Fitness Dual Position Arm Curl and Triceps Machine - Plate Loaded for Versatile Arm Training 
The Dual Position Arm Curl and Triceps Machine is the ultimate plate-loaded bicep and triceps trainer, targeting biceps, triceps, and forearm muscles for effective arm strength and definition. This versatile machine features 28 sundial adjustments, allowing you to customize resistance for your fitness goals. Designed for both push and pull movements, it offers dedicated handles for triceps extensions and bicep curls, ensuring it functions as a dual position arm curl machine and a tricep extension machine. 
With three grip positions, this multi-position biceps and triceps trainer adds variety and allows you to isolate specific muscle groups for a well-rounded workout. Built with durable materials, this ergonomic arm curl and triceps bench ensures proper form and reduces strain, making it ideal for home gyms or light-commercial setups. Building strength, improving definition, or enhancing performance, this adjustable arm workout machine is your go-to for achieving your fitness goals.

description: Our Flarhetoric 2-in-1 roman chair and preacher curl bench combines the functions and advantages of both machines together, providing whole-body workout from arms, back, waist, ab, glute to legs.Four Adjustable Parts:Foam Foot Holder: 2 Positions Barbell & Dumbbell Holders: 5 Positions (17"-21")Preacher Curl Pad: 5 Positions (14"-20") Seat: 5 Positions (28"-33")Crafted from durable and high quality steel, this hyperextension bench can support a weight capacity up to 440lbs. features: 【Multifunctional Workout】With preacher curl bench and roman chair combined, this multifunctional workout machine not only allows you to do the bicep curl with barbells and dumbbells for grip and forearm strength, but also the hyperextension workout to strengthen lower back, glute, leg and hamstring muscles.

【Durable Material & Stable Structure】Crafted from durable and high quality steel, this hyperextension bench can support a weight capacity up to 440lbs. The triangular structure, U shaped base and anti-slip stabilizers ensure the stability of the machine when you are training.

【Adjustable Height for Fitness】Our roman chair has four parts of adjustable heights to help you find the best position for excellent and effective workout experience. The Foam Foot Holder has 2 adjustable positions, while the barbell & dumbbell holders, the preacher curl pad and the seat cushion all have 5 adjustable positions.

【Comfortable & Thoughtful Design】With the barbell holders, the preacher curl bench and roman chair allows you to do the bicep curl exercise with barbell conveniently. The foam foot holder and the anti-slip foot pedals help hold your legs in place, keeping exercise more effective.

【Easy to Assemble】 The adjustable strength training bench will come with clear instruction, making it easy to be assembled or installed. If you have any question or problem during the assembling process, please feel free to let us know and we are willing to offer help.

title: Jayflex Hyperbell Dumbbell Converter - Convert Dumbbells to Barbell Set and Kettlebell for Home Fitness - Adjustable & Up to 200 lb Capacity Weight Barbell for Weight Lifting
inStockText: In Stock  Only 3 left in stock - order soon.
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Bars
description: Transform your home gym into the ultimate fitness center with the Jayflex Hyperbell Bar. This amazing adjustable dumbbell set allows you to work from home, without the need for extra equipment or space. The Hyperbell Bar has multi-purpose high-quality steel connectors that allow you to convert your dumbbells into a full barbell set. The Hyperbell Bar can handle weights of up to 200 lbs, with each side of the dumbbell connector bar capable of holding up to 100 lb weights. With the weight lifting bar included in the set, you can easily create a challenging workout that helps you reach your goals. Built with high-strength modular plastic clamps, the Hyperbell Bar has been stringently tested for durability in the toughest workouts. The bar is perfect for serious strength training and can be used for bench presses, deadlifts, and power cleans. Incorporating the Hyperbell Bar into your home fitness routine is easy. Simply snap your chosen weights into the dumbbell attachments on the weight bar to create a versatile workout routine. The weight-adjustable home barbell connectors are foam-lined for a safe and secure grip. The Hyperbell Bar is ideal for home gym workouts and is compatible with most standard hex dumbbells, including Bowflex SelectTech, CORE Fitness, Peloton, JaxJox, MX Select, Merax, and NordicTrack (orange version). However, it is not compatible with PowerBlock, NordicTrack (blue version), or Nuobell dumbbells. Whether you're looking to intensify your squats, lunges, curls, and rows, or target the chest, shoulders, and biceps with bench presses and military presses, the Hyperbell Bar is the perfect addition to your home gym. Order now and take the first step towards achieving your fitness goals!

WORK FROM HOME FITNESS: The perfect addition to your home gym equipment, this weight lifting bar allows you to work on your fitness from the comfort of your own home.

ADJUSTABLE DUMBBELLS: The dumbbell barbell converter fits most standard and adjustable dumbbell weight sets with straight or curved handles up to 1.5” thick and minimum of 4.5” long, providing dumbbells adjustable weight for your workout needs.

BARBELL SET: Incorporate this weight bar into your home gym for bar weights and barbell weights to take your lifting and strength training to the next level with squat bar and bench press bar exercises.

HOME WEIGHT SET: Enjoy gym weights for home with this versatile dumbbell to barbells converter, compatible with rubber dumbbells, Bowflex SelectTech adjustable dumbbells, and other brands for a comprehensive home gym solution.

Previous page
Next page
Can the ShredForce be used for leg workouts too? 
No - the ShredForce is specifically made to help you train your upper body, so it won't be safe to use as a leg trainer. 
When storing my ShredForce, should it be open or closed? 
The best way to store it is to lower the resistance level and close the arm exerciser. This way your hydraulics will stay in outstanding condition for much longer. 
Do the hydraulics on the exerciser leak oil during training? 
Absolutely not. The premium hydraulics built into the ShredForce are durable and made to feel absolutely outstanding during workouts - no leaks, no other issues. 
Who can benefit from the ShredForce? 
The compact form combined with a wide resistance range makes the ShredForce a great option for traveling athletes, people just getting back into training, folks who live in smaller spaces, and anyone who needs an extra boost of upper body strength. 
Will the ShredForce replace my dumbbells? 
While most people will be perfectly satisfied with the upper body workouts they can perform with the Shredforce, it isn't made to be a direct replacement for dumbbells, but rather a complement that covers the needs your dumbbells don't.

title: Seated Dip Machine Plate Loaded- Tricep Dip Press Machine with Cable Bar for Biceps Chest Training, Hold up to 400LBS
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Upper Body Machines
features: [Versatile Upper Body Training Machine]- The seated triceps dip machine allows for focused and isolated workouts. Its convergent motion ensures that the triceps muscles are activated for maximum exercise effectiveness. In addition, the triceps press machine comes with a cable bar for doing biceps exercises like upright cable rows and biceps curls. It's a versatile machine that engages the muscles of the arms, shoulder and chest to take your upper body strength training to the next level!

[Improved Arms and Machine Design]- The seated dip machine is a safer and more effective alternative to traditional tricep dips, which can cause strain on the wrists and shoulders. With stable and controllable movements, this seated dip station minimizes the risk of injuries. Additionally, the tricep pushdown machine features a rotating handle that can be adjusted to fit varying shoulder widths, providing multiple grip options to target different areas of the triceps muscles.

[Personalized Adjustments]- It offers easy-to-use personalization adjustments, allowing you to customize your workout to suit your varying fitness levels and training goals with simple weight plate adjustments. Even beginners can experience challenging workouts without requiring extensive technical skills or coordination. The seat height and cable bar length can be adjusted to accommodate different body types, ensuring maximum comfort and efficiency during your exercise routine.

[High Quality Material]- The plate loaded tricep machine is composed of heavy-duty steel and premium coatings, making it durable and stable. The comfortable, sweat-resistant seat and backrest provide ample support for intense workouts and long-term use. Measuring only 42.7"x26.2"x51.2", it's the ideal size for any space in your home gym. With a maximum weight capacity of 400 LBS and compatibility with 1" and 2" weight plates, it can meet your most daily training needs. (Plates are not included)

[Easy to Use Step]- The tricep press machine is also featured by simplicity in use. To give your triceps a serious workout, all you need to do is choose the right weights, adjust the seat height, and grab onto the narrow handles. If you want to give your lower chest muscles some extra attention, just lean forward ever so slightly and switch to the wide handle. To perform a bicep curl, rise to your feet and plant them firmly on a rugged steel plate, then you can exercise freely with cable handle.

features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

OPTIMIZE YOUR WORKOUT - The Body-Solid Tools Pro-Grip V-Bar is designed for maximum efficiency. Its center-balanced construction and ergonomic design allow for a full range of motion, ensuring continuous and consistent tension throughout all biceps and triceps exercises.

ENHANCED GRIP - This Pro-Grip V-Bar comes with two rubber grips to ensure no-slip comfort and control when you're pushing your limits. Ideal for use with any cable attachment system, it's made of heavy-duty solid steel with a chrome finish for durability.

EXPERTLY DESIGNED FOR PERFORMANCE - The Body-Solid Tools Pro-Grip V-Bar is expertly designed for high-performance strength training. Ideal for exercises like tricep pressdowns, barbell curls, and lat pulldowns, this versatile gym attachment enhances your workout by providing continuous, consistent tension.

VERSATILITY AND DURABILITY - The Body-Solid Tools Pro-Grip V-Bar is a versatile piece of gym equipment that can be used with various cable machine systems for a wide array of strength training exercises. Weighing 7 pounds and made from solid steel with a sleek chrome finish.

description: Transform the Body-Solid GPR400 power rack into a complete home gym with the GLA400 lat attachment. The attachment allows users to perform high and low pulley exercises including lat pulldowns, rows, biceps curls, shrugs and more in the comfort and stability of a power rack. Unique design allows the lat attachment to fit into the GPR400 without requiring additional space or clearance around the rack. The GLA400 is a plate-loaded attachment allowing users to easily add weight plates. It’s compatible with Body-Solid’s SP150 150 lb. weight stack. Nylon-coated, aircraft quality cables ensure durability and safety while using the GLA400. This product features a Lifetime for in-home, personal usage. Pads, pulleys, cables, frames, and everything in between is covered for as long as you own the equipment. This product is Commercial Rated and features a Lifetime on frames, welds, weight plates & guide rods. 3 Years on pulleys, bushing, bearings & hardware. 1 Year on cables, upholstery, grips and all other components.
features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, power rack, strength training smith machine, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

CABLE ATTACHMENT FOR VARIOUS WORKOUTS: Discover the unparalleled convenience of this lat and row bar attachment. Perform multiple high and low pulley exercises including lat pulldowns, rows, and bicep curls. Never miss a workout given your busy schedule. Unlock full-body workouts with ease and attain your fitness goals without stepping out of your comfort zone.

POWERFUL PERFORMANCE IN A COMPACT DESIGN: Seamlessly integrated into your GPR400 Power Rack for a more extensive workout option. Perfect for any home, from expansive gym rooms to cozy apartments. The GLA400 is a plate-loaded attachment allowing users to easily add weight plates to the GLA400. So, you can focus on multiple upper body muscles from biceps, triceps, shoulders, to back.

COMPREHENSIVE MUSCLE TARGETING: This cable exercise attachment enables targeted strength training that promotes muscle growth and toning from the comfort of your home. Enjoy the freedom of crafting workouts that align perfectly with your fitness goals; every extension, curl, and shrug designed to elevate your physique, performance, and overall well-being.

ACHIEVE UNMATCHED STABILITY AND SAFETY: With the GLA400 designed specifically for the Body-Solid GPR400 Power Rack, stability in every workout is guaranteed. Experience worry-free exercises, knowing your equipment is engineered for safety and durability.

title: Best Fitness Semi Recumbent AB Crunch Bench (BFAB20R), Lower & Upper Abdominal Muscles Workout Machine For Home Gym, Red/Black
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Benches › Adjustable Benches
description: Product DescriptionPerform a variety of ab exercises easily, effectively, and safely with the Body-Solid Best Fitness Semi Recumbent AB Bench (BFAB20). The adjustable, ergonomic AB crunch bench seat can be adjusted into 3 different positions to accommodate a wide range of heights and motion. The AB workout bench seat is angled at 45-degrees and reclines to 2 different 5-degree angles for a wide range of motion. This abdominal bench with adjustable length, textured grip handles, standard weight post, and 2-position footrests make it is comfortable and easy to perform exercises such as ab crunches and knee raises. When assembled the Body-Solid Best Fitness Semi Recumbent AB Bench (BFAB20) measures 64 by 11 by 46 inches (L x W x H). The frame is backed by the Best Fitness 3-year Warranty and the parts are backed by a 1 year warranty.Amazon.comMake any time crunch time with the Best Fitness BFAB20 semi-recumbent ab crunch. Unlike some other ab machines--which require the agility of an acrobat to be thoroughly effective--the BFAB20 puts you in a comfortable seated position without sacrificing your workout efficiency. The ergonomically designed machine is built to help you tighten up your midsection, strengthen your back, and improve your core stability, with your choice of toning your lower abs with knees raises or your upper abs with abdominal crunches. To perform ab crunches, simply use the upholstered upper back support, textured grip handles, and standard weight post. Performing knee raises is just as easy thanks to the adjustable-length, two-position footrests. Add in a three-position upholstered seat--which starts at 45 degrees but offers two additional 5-degree reclining positions--and you have everything you need to design an effective ab regimen in the comfort of your own home.  The BFAB20 is an essential workout accessory because your core is where all your body movements originate. Your abdominal muscles support and protect your internal organs and aid in breathing, especially when you exhale. The abs also team up with your back muscles to control trunk motions, such as twisting and bending. The BFAB20 takes the next step by also strengthening and toning the front of the thighs and increasing hip flexibility. The end results include a flatter stomach, better defined abs, well-developed obliques, a more upright posture, and greater support for your spine. Other features include a 1.75-inch upholstered seat, a durable powder-coated finish, and safety pins and bolts that allow for easy disassembly or permanent setup. The BFAB20 measures 22 by 46 by 64 inches (W x H x D) and carries a three-year warranty.
features: "INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Best FItness by Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life."

"ERGONOMICALLY DESIGNED: This ergonomically designed machine is built to help you tighten up your midsection, strengthen your back and improve your core stability. Its dual functionality lets you target your lower abs with knee raises and your upper abs with abdominal crunches."

"45-DEGREE WORKOUT SEAT: This machine can provide total ab workout from a comfortable seated position. The 45-degree seat angle puts you in position to isolate your abdominal muscles, for a more efficient workout. Plus, with two additional 5-degree reclining positions, you'll be ideally supported for an entire range of core exercises."

"ADJUSTABLE FOOT RESTS: The adjustable foot rests can be adjusted up to 13 different positions including 3 height adjustments and 10 slope level adjustments providing maximum comfort, stability and most importantly, target the right muscle groups for desired results. Plus, with the ergonomic handlebars and padded cushion, you'll be able to get the most out of your session without sacrificing on comfort."

"DIMENSIONS: This ab machine is perfect for those just starting out their core-training journey or for more experienced athletes, as the adjustable tension knob can be easily adjusted to match your preferred challenge level. The measures 22 x 46 x 64 inches and carries a three-year warrantty on the frame and 1 year on ALL parts."

description: A cable machine attachment is an essential piece of equipment for anyone serious about strength training and building muscle. This versatile accessory attaches to a cable pulley system, allowing you to perform a wide range of exercises that target specific muscle groups. With the ability to adjust the resistance and angle of pull, you can customize your workout to focus on areas like your chest, back, shoulders, arms, and legs. The cable machine attachment provides a smooth and controlled motion, reducing stress on your joints while still challenging your muscles. Whether you're looking to sculpt your physique, improve your strength, or enhance your overall fitness, this attachment offers a comprehensive and effective solution. Incorporate it into your routine and experience the benefits of targeted, resistance-based training
features: THE VLROQA LAT BAR：Perfectly compatible with functional trainers, home gym pulley systems, cable machines and more, making it easier to start exercising
BUILD A BIGGER BACK: Lat Pull Down can be extremely beneficial in building upper body strength especially in strengthening the muscles of the shoulder, latissimus dorsi, biceps and infraspinatus
MATERIAL AND FEATURES: Made of high-strength steel ,features rotating and swiveling center for more sports
NON-SLIP RUBBER HANDLE: Use environment friendly textured rubber to provide ergonomic and firm grip during your regular routine, as well as to increase comfort and safety
WIDE RANGE of APPLICATIONS: Our bar is designed to meet the training needs of people of different skill levels, from beginner to professional

title: Body-Solid Home Gym Tools LAT Pulldown Revolving Curl Bar Attachment for Pulley Cable Machine - Lat Pull Down Curling Bar Accessories for Fitness, Strength Workout Equipment, Muscle Building
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Bars
description: Add functionality to your Body-Solid home gym system with the Body-Solid Tools Revolving Curl Bar (MB229). Featuring an angled design that specifically isolates your biceps and triceps muscles, this curling bar allows you to reach peak concentration in your bicep curl workout, so you can achieve the most complete arm development possible.This curl barbell is made of durable solid steel with a knurled grip in the center and edges of the bar. This allows for close- and wide-grip curls as well as triceps press downs with exceptional control and balance. The Body-Solid Tools Revolving Curl Bar measures 29 inches in length and weighs 7 pounds.
features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

Non Slip & Secure Grip: The perfect addition to your home gym and weight loss routine. Our straight bar is designed to provide a comfortable and secure grip, allowing for maximum bicep development during your lifting sessions. Our bar is made from heavy grade aluminum, making it sturdy and durable for even the most intense routines.

Great For Upper Body & Core Training: The cable attachments for gym is designed to build strength and muscles in the upper body by focusing exercise on shoulders, back, lats, triceps, biceps and abs. Incorporate this bar into your home gym and start for your V-shape body!

Cable Machine Accessories: Our cable machine accessories are designed to have a secure fit, allowing for maximum control when using the machine. We offer a wide range of accessories, including cable curls, leg press attachments, and chest flies, giving your home gym an extra level of customization.

Premium Material: Our lat pull down bar provides additional strength and durability to your workout routine. Constructed with solid steel, our lat bar is far more heavy-duty than plastic or wooden lat bars. It is designed to have a strong grip, allowing for maximum muscle activation during your lat pull down routine.

Customize your comfort with adjustable armrest pads, seat height, and barbell holder to fit various body shapes. Enjoy the thickened, sweat-resistant preacher curl pad as you push limits on this versatile bicep tricep curl machine, supporting up to 265 pounds. Comfortable Pad: Equipped with a 3.1" thick preacher curl pad, this bicep curl machine ensures protection for both your chest and elbows during workouts, while the sweat-resistant PU cover adds durability and comfort.
Strong Structure: Our bicep tricep curl machine supports a max load of 265 pounds and is constructed with solid steel tubing and non-slip foot covers, ensuring longevity and stability.
Versatile Workouts: Suitable for both dumbbell and barbell biceps routines, this bicep machine is great for enhancing your arm workouts and building strength in your biceps and triceps.
